      "side": 1,
      "message": "It looks like the purpose of this code block is to flesh out a short phone# by prepending the appropriate amount of digits from the phone prefix to it. With that in mind, I think it might make more sense to generalize the logic here a bit. I\u0027ll add asserts to make sure that the phone number prefix is within valid limits (it shouldn\u0027t be possible for get_phone_number_prefix to return strings that violate this anyways).\n\nDo you know if modem\u0027s current tests exercise this code path at all?",
